## Notes on bundled third-party material

This pack bundles material from several upstream MIT-licensed projects, each of
which retains its own copyright and license notice in its respective
subdirectory:

- `skills/_vendor/` — vendor skills, MIT, see `skills/_vendor/LICENSE`
- `examples/line-ai-customer-service-onprem/` — derived from
  `scorpioliu0953/ai_customer_service`, MIT, see the example's `LICENSE` and
  `CREDITS.md`
- `examples/line-ai-customer-service/` — derived from the same upstream, with
  attribution in the example's `CREDITS.md`
- `examples/google-workspace-admin-workflow/` — derived from
  `mihozip/google-workspace-admin-project-workflow`, with attribution in the
  example's `CREDITS.md` and `PROVENANCE.md` (line-pinned to upstream commit)

See `THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md` for the full list and attribution chain.
